```{r, echo=FALSE}
accessory <- read.csv("./data/EXTR_Accessory_V.csv")

accessory <- accessory %>% 
  mutate(mm_key = paste0(Major, '-', Minor), .before = 1) %>% 
  select(-c(Major, Minor, AccyDescr, UpdatedBy, UpdateDate))

accessory <- accessory %>% 
  filter(Size >= 0)

accessory$AccyType <- as.factor(accessory$AccyType)
```
